headline.print_headline: Man Killed After Falling Into Wood Chipper in Arizona
headline.main: Man Killed After Falling Into Wood Chipper in Arizona

lead_paragraph: A landscape gardener was decapitated after falling into a wood chipper in Arizona on Thursday and a police spokesman said no foul play was suspected.
